commit.message:
2016-08-23  Venkataramanan Kumar

	* config/i386/i386.c (processor_alias_table): Enable PTA_PRFCHW
	for targets amdfam10 and barcelona.

From-SVN: r239682

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@
+2016-08-23  Venkataramanan Kumar
+
+	* config/i386/i386.c (processor_alias_table): Enable PTA_PRFCHW
+	for targets amdfam10 and barcelona.
+
 2016-08-22  Uros Bizjak  <ubizjak@gmail.com>
 
 	* config/i386/i386.md (*zero_extendsidi2): Add (*r,*k) alternative.

@@ -4958,10 +4958,10 @@ ix86_option_override_internal (bool main_args_p,
 	| PTA_SSE2 | PTA_NO_SAHF | PTA_FXSR},
       {"amdfam10", PROCESSOR_AMDFAM10, CPU_AMDFAM10,
 	PTA_64BIT | PTA_MMX | PTA_3DNOW | PTA_3DNOW_A | PTA_SSE | PTA_SSE2
-	| PTA_SSE3 | PTA_SSE4A | PTA_CX16 | PTA_ABM | PTA_FXSR},
+	| PTA_SSE3 | PTA_SSE4A | PTA_CX16 | PTA_ABM | PTA_FXSR | PTA_PRFCHW},
       {"barcelona", PROCESSOR_AMDFAM10, CPU_AMDFAM10,
 	PTA_64BIT | PTA_MMX | PTA_3DNOW | PTA_3DNOW_A | PTA_SSE | PTA_SSE2
-	| PTA_SSE3 | PTA_SSE4A | PTA_CX16 | PTA_ABM | PTA_FXSR},
+	| PTA_SSE3 | PTA_SSE4A | PTA_CX16 | PTA_ABM | PTA_FXSR | PTA_PRFCHW},
       {"bdver1", PROCESSOR_BDVER1, CPU_BDVER1,
 	PTA_64BIT | PTA_MMX | PTA_SSE | PTA_SSE2 | PTA_SSE3
 	| PTA_SSE4A | PTA_CX16 | PTA_ABM | PTA_SSSE3 | PTA_SSE4_1
